<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:ttp="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#parameter" xmlns:composer="https://composer.boidu.dev/ttml" ttp:timeBase="media" xml:lang="en" composer:timing="Line"><head><metadata><ttm:title>beastboy - 2HEAVY</ttm:title><ttm:agent xml:id="v1" type="person"><ttm:name>Beastboy</ttm:name></ttm:agent><ttm:agent xml:id="v2" type="other"><ttm:name>Bob Danvers-Walker</ttm:name></ttm:agent></metadata></head><body dur="2:47.008"><div><p begin="0:04.287" end="0:05.248" ttm:agent="v2">Never stops working</p><p begin="0:05.606" end="0:07.270" ttm:agent="v2">Ceramist, sculptor, painter</p><p begin="0:07.270" end="0:10.769" ttm:agent="v2">In one medium or another the flow of his artistic output is unceasing</p><p begin="0:11.468" end="0:15.178" ttm:agent="v1">Prince of worry, prince of worry</p><p begin="0:23.530" end="0:27.115" ttm:agent="v1">Der Donner lässt sie wissen, dass der Boy zurück ist</p><p begin="0:27.412" end="0:30.730" ttm:agent="v1">Mit knurrendem Magen stepp' ich in Teufels Küche<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="0:30.909" end="0:31.277">Huh</span></span></p><p begin="0:31.318" end="0:33.294" ttm:agent="v1">Lesson learned, back to work</p><p begin="0:33.294" end="0:37.131" ttm:agent="v1">Baby, so wie's aussieht, heißt es ab jetzt us against the world<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="0:37.143" end="0:37.443">Wouh</span></span></p><p begin="0:37.531" end="0:40.422" ttm:agent="v1">Ich hab' von meinem Leben so viel preisgegeben</p><p begin="0:40.422" end="0:42.697" ttm:agent="v1">Meinе Fehltritte breit gеtreten</p><p begin="0:42.697" end="0:45.541" ttm:agent="v1">Meinetwegen soll'n sie ihre Scheiße reden<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="0:45.037" end="0:46.312">Huh, huh, huh</span></span></p><p begin="0:46.264" end="0:49.621" ttm:agent="v1">Ich liefer' euch Gossip für eure Online-Soap</p><p begin="0:49.621" end="0:53.561" ttm:agent="v1">Ihr werdet euch alle noch schäm'n, wenn der Tod euch holt<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="0:53.537" end="0:54.214">Ah</span></span></p><p begin="0:54.581" end="0:56.414" ttm:agent="v1">He will put you in your place</p><p begin="0:56.414" end="0:59.974" ttm:agent="v1">In kei'm Bunker bist du safe, wenn deine Stunde einmal schlägt</p><p begin="0:59.974" end="1:03.962" ttm:agent="v1">Versuch das Universe zu play'n und du gehst unter in den Waves</p><p begin="1:03.978" end="1:07.758" ttm:agent="v1">Wir sind mehr als ein elektrischer Impuls in unserm Brain</p><p begin="1:07.799" end="1:11.993" ttm:agent="v1">Egal, ob Gott oder Kosmos, it's too big for us<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="1:11.968" end="1:12.414">Wouh</span></span></p><p begin="1:12.486" end="1:15.798" ttm:agent="v1">Nach 'nem Wimpernschlag liegen wir schon in 'nem Sarg<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="1:15.750" end="1:16.294">Hah</span></span></p><p begin="1:16.258" end="1:19.587" ttm:agent="v1">Ohne Yin im Yang, siehst du immer schwarz<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="1:17.718" end="1:18.146">Hah,</span><span begin="1:19.587" end="1:20.010"> Hah</span></span></p><p begin="1:20.020" end="1:23.276" ttm:agent="v1">Ohne Gnade kreist der Zeiger übers Ziffernblatt<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="1:23.354" end="1:23.939">Wouh</span></span></p><p begin="1:23.755" end="1:27.598" ttm:agent="v1">Life is pain, life is torture, life is strange, life's a blessing</p><p begin="1:27.598" end="1:30.335" ttm:agent="v1">Life is precious, life is borderline insane</p><p begin="1:30.437" end="1:34.159" ttm:agent="v1">Life is madness, life is balance, life is family rebellions</p><p begin="1:34.218" end="1:37.987" ttm:agent="v1">Life is realizing that you copy habits of your parents</p><p begin="1:37.987" end="1:41.182" ttm:agent="v1">Life's a bitch, slut, thot, call it what you want</p><p begin="1:41.182" end="1:44.100" ttm:agent="v1">Life is tears and blood, we don't need no plug</p><p begin="1:44.100" end="1:45.509" ttm:agent="v1">Life's a fucking drug</p><p begin="1:45.509" end="1:48.836" ttm:agent="v1">Life's a bitch, slut, thot, call it what you want<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="1:46.268" end="1:46.511">Bitch</span> <span begin="1:46.743" end="1:47.000">Slut</span> <span begin="1:47.237" end="1:47.487">Thot</span></span></p><p begin="1:48.836" end="1:51.656" ttm:agent="v1">We don't need no plug, life's a fucking drug</p><p begin="1:51.656" end="1:53.528" ttm:agent="v1">Life's a fucking drug Boy<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="1:54.081" end="1:54.381">Boy</span></span></p><p begin="1:54.549" end="1:57.535" ttm:agent="v1">Raise your fists, stand against the deadly sins</p><p begin="1:57.535" end="2:01.274" ttm:agent="v1">You're gonna break your limbs, when you walk the way of kings</p><p begin="2:01.274" end="2:04.437" ttm:agent="v1">I had to bow, 'cause the crown was too heavy</p><p begin="2:04.437" end="2:06.818" ttm:agent="v1">The-the crown was too hea-hea-hea-hea-</p><p begin="2:06.818" end="2:08.912" ttm:agent="v2">Running water never grows stale</p><p begin="2:09.664" end="2:12.572" ttm:agent="v1">Raise your fists, stand against the deadly sins<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="2:09.187" end="2:09.697">Ah</span></span></p><p begin="2:12.873" end="2:16.228" ttm:agent="v1">You're gonna break your limbs, when you walk the way of kings<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="2:12.587" end="2:13.017">Ah</span></span></p><p begin="2:16.515" end="2:19.613" ttm:agent="v1">I had to bow, 'cause the crown was too heavy<span ttm:role="x-bg"><span begin="2:16.287" end="2:16.626">Ah</span></span></p><p begin="2:19.724" end="2:23.478" ttm:agent="v1">But now I am ready, no-no-now I am ready</p><p begin="2:23.651" end="2:25.606" ttm:agent="v1">And don't get me wrong, I don't want this no more</p><p begin="2:25.606" end="2:27.530" ttm:agent="v1">Stop the applause, fuck the awards</p><p begin="2:27.530" end="2:28.998" ttm:agent="v1">I never was who you thought I was</p><p begin="2:28.998" end="2:30.845" ttm:agent="v1">And I will never be, 'cause there is more to us</p><p begin="2:30.845" end="2:33.045" ttm:agent="v1">Than what all of us perceive with the human eye</p><p begin="2:33.045" end="2:34.920" ttm:agent="v1">The human mind should have a user guide</p><p begin="2:35.137" end="2:36.824" ttm:agent="v1">It won't be easy to cheer for yourself</p><p begin="2:36.824" end="2:38.932" ttm:agent="v1">Or feel for yourself if you fear yourself</p></div></body></tt>